name: Father of My Child
description:
"Good Morning My Love, Did You Sleep Well?" series no.3
This belongs to a series of three pieces.

•Lovers•
I saw my reflection in his eyes as I was dying in his hands. I looked helpless and in love with the father of my child that I was carrying. He promised to help me with the kid! I guess it's was the way of his help. he could have helped me just get rid of this baby not to get rid of both of us.
